EDUCATIONAL USE NOTICE:

This software is designed as an educational technology platform for academic
purposes. While commercial use is permitted under the MIT License, users are
encouraged to:

1. Maintain educational accessibility and WCAG 2.1 AA compliance standards
2. Preserve attribution to EOPeak and the original educational mission
3. Consider contributing improvements back to the educational community
4. Respect student privacy and educational data protection standards

