PROFESSIONAL SERVICES:

EOPeak specializes in transforming traditional academic materials (PDFs, Word documents,
slides, and spreadsheets) into fast, responsive, interactive, and downloadable web-based
learning environments. This project serves as a demonstration of enterprise-grade
educational technology capabilities.

Services include:
- Academic Material Conversion (PDF to Interactive Web)
- Educational Platform Development
- Progressive Web Application (PWA) Creation
- Accessibility Implementation (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- Performance Optimization for Educational Content
- Learning Management System (LMS) Integration

